18 bool TreeNode::operator==(const TreeNode &node) const {
19 if(this->left != nullptr && node.left == nullptr) {
20 return false;
21 }
22 if(this->left == nullptr && node.left != nullptr) {
23 return false;
24 }
25 if(this->right != nullptr && node.right == nullptr) {
26 return false;
27 }
28 if(this->right == nullptr && node.right != nullptr) {
29 return false;
30 }
31 if(this->left != nullptr && node.left != nullptr && *this->left != *node.left) {
32 return false;
33 }
34 if(this->right != nullptr && node.right != nullptr && *this->right != *node.right) {
35 return false;
36 }
37 return this->val == node.val;
38 }
39
40 bool TreeNode::operator!=(const TreeNode &node) const { return !(*this == node); }

43 vector<string> Solution::findAllConcatenatedWordsInADict(vector<string> &words) {
44 sort(words.begin(), words.end(), [&](const string &a, const string &b) { return a.size() < b.size(); });
45 auto ans = vector<string>();
46 auto node = TrieNode(0);
47 for(const string &word: words) {
48 if(word.length() == 0) {
49 continue;
50 }
51 if(node.dfs(&node, word, 0, false)) {
52 ans.push_back(word);
53 } else {
54 node.insert(word);
55 }
56 }
57 return ans;
58 }

60 TrieNode::TrieNode(char ch) {
61 this->ch = ch;
62 this->is_end = false;
63 }
64
65 void TrieNode::insert(const string &str) {
66 auto *node = this->nexts[str[0] - 'a'];
67 if(node == nullptr) {
68 node = new TrieNode(str[0]);
69 this->nexts[str[0] - 'a'] = node;
70 }
71 if(str.length() == 1) {
72 node->is_end = true;
73 return;
74 }
75 return node->insert(str.substr(1));
76 }
77
78 bool TrieNode::dfs(TrieNode *root, const string &str, int start, bool flag) const {
79 if(this->ch == 0) {
80 //根节点
81 auto *const node = this->nexts[str[start] - 'a'];
82 if(node == nullptr) {
83 return false;
84 }
85 return node->dfs(root, str, start, flag);
86 }
87 //非根节点
88 //到一个单词结束处
89 if(this->is_end) {
90 if(start == str.length() - 1) {
91 return flag;
92 }
93 const auto res = root->dfs(root, str, start + 1, true);
94 if(res) {
95 return true;
96 }
97 }
98 TrieNode *node = nullptr;
99 if(str[start + 1] - 'a' >= 0) {
100 node = this->nexts[str[start + 1] - 'a'];
101 }
102 return node != nullptr && node->dfs(root, str, start + 1, flag);
103 }

117 namespace excel_sheet_column_title {
118 string Solution::convertToTitle(int columnNumber) {
119 auto ans = string();
120 bool round = false;
121 while(columnNumber != 0) {
122 char ch = 0;
123 if(round) {
124 ch = static_cast<char>(columnNumber % 26 + 63);
125 round = false;
126 } else {
127 ch = static_cast<char>(columnNumber % 26 + 64);
128 }
129 if(ch == '@' && columnNumber >= 26) {
130 ch = 'Z';
131 round = true;
132 } else if(ch == '?' && columnNumber >= 26) {
133 ch = 'Y';
134 round = true;
135 }
136 if('A' <= ch && ch <= 'Z') {
137 ans.insert(0, 1, ch);
138 }
139 columnNumber /= 26;
140 }
141 return ans;
142 }

163 namespace count_special_quadruplets {
164 int Solution::countQuadruplets(vector<int> &nums) {
165 int sum = 0;
166 for(int i = 3; i < nums.size(); i++) {
167 for(int j = 0; j < i - 2; j++) {
168 if(j == i) {
169 continue;
170 }
171 for(int k = j + 1; k < i - 1; k++) {
172 if(k == i) {
173 continue;
174 }
175 for(int l = k + 1; l < i; l++) {
176 if(l == i) {
177 continue;
178 }
179 if(nums[k] + nums[j] + nums[l] == nums[i]) {
180 sum++;
181 }
182 }
183 }
184 }
185 }
186 return sum;
187 }

190 namespace hand_of_straights {
191 bool Solution::isNStraightHand(vector<int> &hand, int groupSize) {
192 if(hand.size() % groupSize != 0) {
193 return false;
194 }
195 if(groupSize == 1) {
196 return true;
197 }
198 sort(hand.begin(), hand.end());
199 const auto len = hand.size() / groupSize;
200 for(int i = 0; i < len; i++) {
201 int current = *hand.begin();
202 hand.erase(hand.begin());
203 for(int j = 1; j < groupSize; j++) {
204 auto next = find(hand.begin(), hand.end(), current + 1);
205 if(next == hand.end()) {
206 return false;
207 }
208 current = *next;
209 hand.erase(next);
210 }
211 }
212 return true;
213 }
214 }// namespace hand_of_straights

217 bool Solution::checkPerfectNumber(int num) {
218 int sum = 0;
219 int max = num;
220 for(int i = 1; i < max; i++) {
221 if(num % i == 0) {
222 sum += i;
223 if(i != 1) {
224 sum += num / i;
225 }
226 max = num / i;
227 }
228 }
229 return sum == num;

234 TreeNode *Solution::convertBST(TreeNode *root) {
235 if(root == nullptr) {
236 return nullptr;
237 }
238 FriendTreeNode *sum = copy(root);
239 get_sum(sum);
240 sum->val = sum->sum - (sum->left == nullptr ? 0 : sum->left->sum);
241 convert(sum);

245 FriendTreeNode *Solution::copy(TreeNode *node) {
246 auto *ret = new FriendTreeNode(node->val, node);
247 if(node->left != nullptr) {
248 ret->left = copy(node->left);
249 }
250 if(node->right != nullptr) {
251 ret->right = copy(node->right);
252 }
253 return ret;
254 }
255
256 void Solution::get_sum(FriendTreeNode *node) {
257 if(node->left != nullptr) {
258 get_sum(node->left);
259 node->sum += node->left->sum;
260 }
261 if(node->right != nullptr) {
262 get_sum(node->right);
263 node->sum += node->right->sum;
264 }
265 }
266
267 void Solution::convert(FriendTreeNode *sum_node) {
268 if(sum_node->right != nullptr) {
269 sum_node->right->val = sum_node->val - sum_node->friend_node->val -
270 (sum_node->right->left == nullptr ? 0 : sum_node->right->left->sum);
271 convert(sum_node->right);
272 }
273 if(sum_node->left != nullptr) {
274 sum_node->left->val = sum_node->val + sum_node->left->friend_node->val +
275 (sum_node->left->right == nullptr ? 0 : sum_node->left->right->sum);
276 convert(sum_node->left);
277 }
278 sum_node->friend_node->val = sum_node->val;
279 }

301 int Solution::lastRemaining(int n) {
302 int num_amount = n;
303 int loop_cnt = 0;
304 int a0 = 1;//初项
305 int d = 1;//差
306 while(num_amount != 1) {
307 //剩下的数目不为1时

312 // 偶数个数字

314 if(left_to_right) {
315 a0 = a0 + d;
316 } else {
317 a0 = a0;
318 }
319 }
320 loop_cnt++;
321 d *= 2;
322 num_amount /= 2;
323 }
324 return a0;

345 int Solution::numberOfBeams(vector<string> &bank) {
346 if(bank.size() == 1) {
347 return 0;
348 }
349 int count = 0;
350 int i = 0;
351 int count_i = deviceCount(bank[i]);
352 int j = 1;
353 while(i < j && i < bank.size() && j < bank.size()) {
354 if(deviceCount(bank[j]) == 0) {
355 j++;
356 continue;
357 }
358 const int count_j = deviceCount(bank[j]);
359 count += count_i * count_j;

361 i = j;
362 j++;
363 }
364 return count;

473 namespace day_of_the_week {
474 string Solution::dayOfTheWeek(int day, int month, int year) {
475 const string output[] = {"Sunday", "Monday", "Tuesday", "Wednesday", "Thursday", "Friday", "Saturday"};
476 const int dayofmonths[] = {31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31};
477 int count = 5;
478 count += (year - 1971) * 365;
479 count += (year - 1) / 4 - 1970 / 4;
480 for(int m = 0; m < month - 1; m++) {
481 count += dayofmonths[m];
482 }
483 if(month > 2 && year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0) {
484 count++;
485 }
486 count += day - 1;
487 count %= 7;
488 return output[count];
489 }

492 namespace cat_and_mouse {
493 int Solution::catMouseGame(vector<vector<int>> &graph) {
494 this->n = graph.size();
495 this->graph = graph;
496 memset(dp, -1, sizeof dp);
497 return getResult(1, 2, 0);
498 }
499
500 int Solution::getResult(int mouse, int cat, int turns) {
501 if(turns == n * 2) {
502 return DRAW;
503 }
504 if(dp[mouse][cat][turns] < 0) {
505 if(mouse == 0) {
506 dp[mouse][cat][turns] = MOUSE_WIN;
507 } else if(cat == mouse) {
508 dp[mouse][cat][turns] = CAT_WIN;
509 } else {
510 getNextResult(mouse, cat, turns);
511 }
512 }
513 return dp[mouse][cat][turns];
514 }
515
516 void Solution::getNextResult(int mouse, int cat, int turns) {
517 const int curMove = turns % 2 == 0 ? mouse : cat;
518 const int defaultResult = curMove == mouse ? CAT_WIN : MOUSE_WIN;
519 int result = defaultResult;
520 for(int next: graph[curMove]) {
521 if(curMove == cat && next == 0) {
522 continue;
523 }
524 const int nextMouse = curMove == mouse ? next : mouse;
525 const int nextCat = curMove == cat ? next : cat;
526 const int nextResult = getResult(nextMouse, nextCat, turns + 1);
527 if(nextResult != defaultResult) {
528 result = nextResult;
529 if(result != DRAW) {
530 break;
531 }
532 }
533 }
534 dp[mouse][cat][turns] = result;
535 }
536 }// namespace cat_and_mouse

559 string Solution::simplifyPath(const string &path) {
560 auto *const str_cpy = new char[path.size() + 1];
561 memcpy(str_cpy, path.c_str(), path.size() + 1);
562 auto *next = strtok(str_cpy, "/");
563 auto stck = deque<string>();
564 while(next != nullptr) {
565 auto nextstr = string(next);
566 if(nextstr == "..") {
567 if(!stck.empty()) {
568 stck.pop_back();
569 }
570 next = strtok(nullptr, "/");
571 continue;
572 }
573 if(nextstr == ".") {
574 next = strtok(nullptr, "/");
575 continue;
576 }
577 stck.emplace_back(next);
578 next = strtok(nullptr, "/");
579 }
580 auto oss = ostringstream();
581 if(stck.empty()) {
582 oss << '/';
583 } else {
584 while(!stck.empty()) {
585 auto pname = stck.front();
586 oss << '/' << pname;
587 stck.pop_front();
588 }
589 }
590 delete[] str_cpy;
591 return oss.str();
592 }

655 namespace minimum_swaps_to_group_all_1s_together_ii {
656 int Solution::minSwaps(vector<int> &nums) {
657 int onecount = 0;
658 for(const int num: nums) {
659 if(num == 1) {
660 onecount++;
661 }
662 }
663 if(onecount == 0) {
664 return 0;
665 }
666
667 int zerocount = 0;
668 for(int i = 0; i < onecount; i++) {
669 if(nums[i] == 0) {
670 zerocount++;
671 }
672 }
673 int min = zerocount;
674
675 for(int i = 0; i < nums.size(); i++) {
676 if(nums[i] == 0) {
677 zerocount--;
678 }
679 if(nums[(onecount + i) % nums.size()] == 0) {
680 zerocount++;
681 }
682 if(zerocount < min) {
683 min = zerocount;
684 }
685 }
686 return min;
687 }

690 namespace count_words_obtained_after_adding_a_letter {
691 int Solution::wordCount(vector<string> &startWords,
692 vector<string> &targetWords) {
693 int count = 0;
694 auto start = unordered_set<unsigned int>();
695 for(const string &word: startWords) {
696 auto bin = str2bin(word);
697 start.insert(bin);
698 }
699 for(const string &word: targetWords) {
700 auto bin = str2bin(word);
701 for(int i = 0; i < 26; i++) {
702 if((bin & 1 << i) != 0 && start.contains(bin - (1 << i))) {
703 //bin有第i个字母且bin去掉第i个字母在start中仍然存在
704 count++;
705 break;
706 }
707 }
708 }
709 return count;
710 }

713 unsigned int ret = 0;
714 for(const char ch: str) {
715 ret |= 1 << ch - 'a';
716 }

740 namespace additive_number {
741 bool Solution::isAdditiveNumber(string num) {
742 if(num.length() < 3) {
743 return false;
744 }
745 auto *const nums = new char[num.length()];
746 for(int i = 0; i < num.length(); i++) {
747 nums[i] = num[i];
748 }
749 for(int i = 1; i <= num.length() - i; i++) {
750 const auto n1 = str2ui(nums, 0, i);
751 for(int j = i + 1; j - i <= num.length() - j; j++) {
752 const auto n2 = str2ui(nums, i, j - i);
753 if(dfs(n1, n2, nums, num.length(), j)) {
754 return true;
755 }
756 if(n2 == 0) {
757 break;
758 }
759 }
760 if(n1 == 0) {
761 break;
762 }
763 }
764 delete[] nums;
765 return false;
766 }
767
768 bool Solution::dfs(unsigned long long n1, unsigned long long n2, const char *nums, unsigned short length, unsigned short current) {
769 const auto sum = to_string(n1 + n2);
770 if(sum.length() > length - current) {
771 //前两位和的位数超过剩余的位数
772 return false;
773 }
774 if(!equal(sum, nums, current, length)) {
775 //不包含下一个数字
776 return false;
777 }
778 if(current + sum.length() == length) {
779 //终止条件
780 return true;
781 }
782 const auto n3 = str2ui(nums, current, sum.length());
783 return dfs(n2, n3, nums, length, current + sum.length());
784 }

787 unsigned long long ans = 0;
788 for(int i = start; i < start + length; i++) {
789 ans *= 10;
790 ans += str[i] - '0';
791 }
792 return ans;
793 }

806 namespace decode_the_slanted_ciphertext {
807 string Solution::decodeCiphertext(string encodedText, int rows) {
808 if(encodedText.empty()) {
809 return "";
810 }
811 const int columns = encodedText.length() / rows;
812 auto *const table = new char *[rows];
813 for(int i = 0; i < rows; i++) {
814 table[i] = new char[columns - rows + 2];
815 for(int j = i; j - i < columns - rows + 2; j++) {
816 if(i * columns + j < encodedText.length()) {
817 table[i][j - i] = encodedText[i * columns + j];
818 } else {
819 table[i][j - i] = ' ';
820 }
821 }
822 }
823 auto oss = ostringstream();
824 for(int j = 0; j < columns - rows + 2; j++) {
825 for(int i = 0; i < rows; i++) {
826 oss << table[i][j];
827 }
828 }
829 string ans = oss.str();
830 for(int i = 0; i < rows; i++) {
831 delete[] table[i];
832 }
833 delete[] table;
834 return rtrim(ans);
835 }

848 namespace escape_a_large_maze {
849 bool Solution::isEscapePossible(vector<vector<int>> &blocked, vector<int> &source, vector<int> &target) {
850 const int limit = blocked.size() * (blocked.size() - 1) / 2;
851 if(blocked.empty()) {
852 return true;
853 }
854 auto *p_source = new point(source[0], source[1], 0, nullptr);
855 auto *p_target = new point(target[0], target[1], 0, nullptr);
856 auto blocked_set_source = unordered_set<point, point_hash>();
857 auto blocked_set_target = unordered_set<point, point_hash>();
858 for(auto block: blocked) {
859 blocked_set_source.insert(point(block[0], block[1], 0, nullptr));
860 blocked_set_target.insert(point(block[0], block[1], 0, nullptr));
861 }
862 const unsigned int source_status = search(blocked_set_source, p_source, p_target, limit);
863 if(source_status == 0) {
864 return false;
865 }
866 if(source_status == 1) {
867 return true;
868 }
869 const unsigned int target_status = search(blocked_set_target, p_target, p_source, limit);
870 delete p_source;
871 delete p_target;
872 return target_status != 0;
873 }
874
875 unsigned int Solution::search(unordered_set<point, point_hash> &block_set, point *source, point *target, unsigned int limit) {
876 auto pq = priority_queue<point>();
877 pq.push(point(source->x, source->y, 0, target));
878 int count = 0;
879 while(!pq.empty()) {
880 if(count > limit || pq.size() > limit) {
881 return 2;//不包围
882 }
883 count++;
884 const auto p = pq.top();
885 pq.pop();
886 point nexts[] = {point(p.x + 1, p.y, p.distance + 1, target), point(p.x - 1, p.y, p.distance + 1, target), point(p.x, p.y + 1, p.distance + 1, target), point(p.x, p.y - 1, p.distance + 1, target)};
887 for(auto next: nexts) {
888 if(0 <= next.x && next.x < 1000000 && 0 <= next.y && next.y < 1000000 && !block_set.contains(next)) {
889 if(next.x == target->x && next.y == target->y) {
890 return 1;//连通
891 }
892 pq.push(next);
893 block_set.insert(next);
894 }
895 }
896 }
897 return 0;//不连通
898 }
899
900 bool point::operator<(const point &p) const { return this->distance + (abs(static_cast<int>(this->x - target->x)) + abs(static_cast<int>(this->y - target->y))) < p.distance + (abs(static_cast<int>(p.x - target->x)) + abs(static_cast<int>(p.y - target->y))); }
901 bool point::operator==(const point &p) const { return this->x == p.x && this->y == p.y; }
902
903 size_t point_hash::operator()(const point &p) const { return p.x * 1000000 + p.y; }
904 }// namespace escape_a_large_maze

906 namespace increasing_triplet_subsequence {
907 bool Solution::increasingTriplet(vector<int> &nums) {
908 if(nums.size() < 3) {
909 return false;
910 }
911 auto *min = new int[nums.size()];
912 auto *max = new int[nums.size()];
913 min[0] = nums[0];
914 max[nums.size() - 1] = nums[nums.size() - 1];
915 for(int i = 1, j = nums.size() - 2; i < nums.size() && j >= 0; i++, j--) {
916 if(min[i - 1] > nums[i]) {
917 min[i] = nums[i];
918 } else {
919 min[i] = min[i - 1];
920 }
921
922 if(max[j + 1] < nums[j]) {
923 max[j] = nums[j];
924 } else {
925 max[j] = max[j + 1];
926 }
927 }
928 for(int i = 0; i < nums.size(); i++) {
929 if(nums[i] > min[i] && nums[i] < max[i]) {
930 delete[] min;
931 delete[] max;
932 return true;
933 }
934 }
935 delete[] min;
936 delete[] max;
937 return false;
938 }

944 return 0;
945 }
946 unsigned int max;
947 unsigned int index;
948 unsigned int second;
949 if(nums[0] < nums[1]) {
950 max = nums[1];
951 index = 1;

956 second = nums[1];

963 } else if(nums[i] > second) {
964 second = nums[i];
965 }

998 namespace permutations {
999 vector<vector<int>> Solution::permute(vector<int> &nums) {
1000 auto ans = vector<vector<int>>();
1001 if(nums.size() == 1) {
1002 auto next_ans = vector<int>();
1003 next_ans.push_back(nums[0]);
1004 ans.push_back(next_ans);
1005 return ans;
1006 }
1007 for(auto num: nums) {
1008 auto next = vector(nums);
1009 next.erase(find(next.begin(), next.end(), num));
1010 auto next_permutations = permute(next);
1011 auto new_ans = vector<int>();
1012 new_ans.push_back(num);
1013 for(auto next_permutation: next_permutations) {
1014 auto next_ans = vector(new_ans);
1015 next_ans.insert(next_ans.end(), next_permutation.begin(), next_permutation.end());
1016 ans.push_back(next_ans);
1017 }
1018 }
1019 return ans;
1020 }

1202 namespace jump_game_iv {
1203 int Solution::minJumps(vector<int> &arr) {
1204 if(arr.size() == 1) {
1205 return 0;
1206 }
1207 auto pq = queue<pair<int, int>>();//<下标,step>
1208 auto *flag = new bool[arr.size()];
1209 memset(flag, 0, arr.size() * sizeof(bool));
1210 auto um = unordered_map<int, vector<int>>();//<值,下标>
1211 for(int i = 0; i < arr.size(); i++) {
1212 if(!um.contains(arr[i])) {
1213 auto vec = vector<int>();
1214 vec.push_back(i);
1215 um.insert(pair(arr[i], vec));
1216 } else {
1217 um[arr[i]].push_back(i);
1218 }
1219 }
1220 pq.push(pair(0, 0));
1221 flag[0] = true;
1222 while(!pq.empty()) {
1223 auto [current_i, current_count] = pq.front();
1224 pq.pop();
1225 if(current_i == arr.size() - 1) {
1226 return current_count;
1227 }
1228 if(um.contains(arr[current_i])) {
1229 for(auto i: um[arr[current_i]]) {
1230 if(i != current_i && !flag[i]) {
1231 pq.push(pair(i, current_count + 1));
1232 flag[i] = true;
1233 }
1234 }
1235 }
1236 um.erase(arr[current_i]);
1237 if(current_i - 1 >= 0 && !flag[current_i - 1]) {
1238 pq.push(pair(current_i - 1, current_count + 1));
1239 flag[current_i - 1] = true;
1240 }
1241 if(current_i + 1 < arr.size() && !flag[current_i + 1]) {
1242 pq.push(pair(current_i + 1, current_count + 1));
1243 flag[current_i + 1] = true;
1244 }
1245 }
1246 delete[] flag;
1247 return 0;
1248 }

1336 namespace k_highest_ranked_items_within_a_price_range {
1337 vector<vector<int>> Solution::highestRankedKItems(vector<vector<int>> &grid, vector<int> &pricing, vector<int> &start, int k) {
1338 const auto m = grid.size();
1339 const auto n = grid[0].size();
1340 auto ans = vector<vector<int>>();
1341 const auto low = pricing[0];
1342 const auto high = pricing[1];
1343 const auto row = start[0];
1344 const auto col = start[1];
1345 auto pq = priority_queue<item>();
1346 pq.push(item(0, grid[row][col], row, col));
1347 grid[row][col] = 0;
1348 while(pq.empty() && k != 0) {
1349 auto current = pq.top();
1350 pq.pop();
1351 if(current.price != 1 && current.price >= low && current.price <= high) {
1352 k--;
1353 auto vec = vector<int>();
1354 vec.push_back(current.row);
1355 vec.push_back(current.col);
1356 ans.push_back(vec);
1357 }
1358 pair<int, int> nexts[4] = {pair(current.row + 1, current.col),
1359 pair(current.row - 1, current.col),
1360 pair(current.row, current.col + 1),
1361 pair(current.row, current.col - 1)};
1362 for(const pair<int, int> next: nexts) {
1363 if(0 <= next.first && next.first < m && 0 <= next.second && next.second < n && grid[next.first][next.second] != 0) {
1364 pq.push(item(current.distance + 1, grid[next.first][next.second], next.first, next.second));
1365 grid[next.first][next.second] = 0;
1366 }
1367 }
1368 }
1369 return ans;
1370 }

1377 return this->price > i.price;

1379 if(this->row != i.row) {

1386 namespace number_of_ways_to_divide_a_long_corridor {
1387 int Solution::numberOfWays(string corridor) {
1388 unsigned int s_count = 0;
1389 auto p = vector<unsigned int>();
1390 for(const char ch: corridor) {
1391 if(ch == 'S') {
1392 s_count++;
1393 }
1394 }
1395 if(s_count == 0 || s_count % 2 != 0) {
1396 return 0;
1397 }
1398 if(s_count == 2) {
1399 return 1;
1400 }
1401 unsigned int start = 0;
1402 unsigned int end = corridor.length() - 1;
1403 for(; start < end; start++) {
1404 if(corridor[start] == 'S') {
1405 break;
1406 }
1407 }
1408 for(; end > start; end--) {
1409 if(corridor[end] == 'S') {
1410 break;
1411 }
1412 }
1413 s_count = 1;
1414 unsigned int p_count = 0;
1415 bool flag = false;//是否在边界
1416 for(unsigned int i = start + 1; i <= end; i++) {
1417 if(corridor[i] == 'S') {
1418 s_count++;
1419 } else {
1420 if(s_count == 0) {
1421 p_count++;
1422 }
1423 }
1424 s_count %= 2;
1425 if(s_count == 0) {
1426 flag = true;
1427 } else if(s_count == 1) {
1428 if(flag) {
1429 p.push_back(p_count + 1);
1430 p_count = 0;
1431 }
1432 flag = false;
1433 }
1434 }
1435 unsigned long long ans = 1;
1436 for(const auto i: p) {
1437 ans *= i;
1438 ans %= 1000000007;
1439 }
1440 return ans;
1441 }
1442 }// namespace number_of_ways_to_divide_a_long_corridor

1505 namespace maximum_good_people_based_on_statements {
1506 int Solution::maximumGood(vector<vector<int>> &statements) {
1507 int maximum = 0;
1508 auto dup = unordered_map<int, bool>();
1509 for(int i = 0; i < statements.size(); i++) {
1510 if(dup[i]) {
1511 continue;
1512 }
1513 const auto um = unordered_map<int, bool>();
1514 auto que = queue<msg>();
1515 que.push(msg(i, true));
1516 auto ans = dfs(statements, um, que);
1517 maximum = max(maximum, ans.first);
1518 for(auto it: ans.second) {
1519 if(it.second) {
1520 dup.insert(it);
1521 }
1522 }
1523 }
1524 return maximum;
1525 }
1526
1527 pair<int, unordered_map<int, bool>> Solution::dfs(vector<vector<int>> &statements, unordered_map<int, bool> um, queue<msg> que) {
1528 int maximum = 0;
1529 bool contradict = false;
1530 while(!que.empty()) {
1531 auto current = que.front();
1532 que.pop();
1533 if(um.contains(current.person)) {
1534 //已经存在
1535 if(um[current.person] != current.good) {
1536 //矛盾
1537 return pair<int, unordered_map<int, bool>>(0, {});
1538 }
1539 } else {
1540 um.insert(pair(current.person, current.good));
1541 }
1542 if(current.good) {
1543 //是好人
1544 for(int j = 0; j < statements.size(); j++) {
1545 if(statements[current.person][j] != 2 && j != current.person) {
1546 auto nmsg = msg(j, statements[current.person][j] == 1);
1547 if(um.contains(nmsg.person)) {
1548 //已经有了
1549 if(um[nmsg.person] != nmsg.good) {
1550 //矛盾
1551 contradict = true;
1552 return pair<int, unordered_map<int, bool>>(0, {});
1553 }
1554 } else {
1555 //还没有
1556 que.push(nmsg);
1557 }
1558 }
1559 }
1560 }
1561 }
1562 if(!contradict) {
1563 //不矛盾
1564 auto dup = unordered_map<int, bool>();
1565 for(int i = 0; i < statements.size(); i++) {
1566 if(dup[i]) {
1567 continue;
1568 }
1569 if(!um.contains(i)) {
1570 bool all2 = true;
1571 for(auto v: statements[i]) {
1572 if(v != 2) {
1573 all2 = false;
1574 }
1575 }
1576 if(all2) {
1577 um.insert(pair(i, true));
1578 continue;
1579 }
1580 auto nque = queue<msg>();
1581 nque.push(msg(i, true));
1582 auto ans = dfs(statements, um, nque);
1583 maximum = max(maximum, ans.first);
1584 for(auto it: ans.second) {
1585 if(it.second) {
1586 dup.insert(it);
1587 }
1588 }
1589 }
1590 }
1591
1592 int good_count = 0;
1593 for(auto i: um) {
1594 if(i.second) {
1595 good_count++;
1596 }
1597 }
1598 maximum = max(maximum, good_count);
1599 }
1600 return pair(maximum, um);
1601 }
1602 }// namespace maximum_good_people_based_on_statements

1627 namespace second_minimum_time_to_reach_destination {
1628 int Solution::secondMinimum(int n, vector<vector<int>> &edges, int time, int change) {
1629 auto record = unordered_map<int, vector<int>>();
1630 for(int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
1631 record.insert(pair(i, vector<int>()));
1632 }
1633 auto um = unordered_map<int, unordered_set<int>>();
1634 for(auto edge: edges) {
1635 if(!um.contains(edge[0])) {
1636 auto us = unordered_set<int>();
1637 us.insert(edge[1]);
1638 um.insert(pair(edge[0], us));
1639 } else {
1640 um[edge[0]].insert(edge[1]);
1641 }
1642 if(!um.contains(edge[1])) {
1643 auto us = unordered_set<int>();
1644 us.insert(edge[0]);
1645 um.insert(pair(edge[1], us));
1646 } else {
1647 um[edge[1]].insert(edge[0]);
1648 }
1649 }
1650 auto pq = priority_queue<status>();
1651 pq.push(status(1, 0));
1652 bool flag = false;//已经到达一次终点
1653 int prev = 0;
1654 while(!pq.empty()) {
1655 status current = pq.top();
1656 pq.pop();
1657 if(current.position == n) {
1658 if(!flag) {
1659 flag = true;
1660 prev = current.time;
1661 } else {
1662 if(current.time != prev) {
1663 return current.time;
1664 }
1665 }
1666 }
1667
1668 if(record[current.position].empty() || record[current.position].size() == 1 && current.time != *record[current.position].rbegin()) {
1669 //可以继续
1670 record[current.position].push_back(current.time);
1671 } else {
1672 continue;
1673 }
1674
1675 for(int next: um[current.position]) {
1676 int next_time;
1677 if(current.time / change % 2 == 1) {
1678 //当前为红灯
1679 next_time = (current.time / change + 1) * change + time;
1680 } else {
1681 next_time = current.time + time;
1682 }
1683 auto next_status = status(next, next_time);
1684 if(record[next_status.position].empty() || record[next_status.position].size() == 1 && next_status.time != *record[next_status.position].rbegin()) {
1685 //可以继续
1686 pq.push(next_status);
1687 }
1688 }
1689 }
1690 return 0;
1691 }
1692
1693 bool status::operator<(const status &s) const { return this->time > s.time; }
1694 }// namespace second_minimum_time_to_reach_destination

1717 int Solution::countValidWords(const string &sentence) {
1718 auto *str = new char[sentence.length() + 1];
1719 strcpy(str, sentence.c_str());
1720 int count = 0;
1721 for(char *token = strtok(str, " "); token != nullptr; token = strtok(nullptr, " ")) {
1722 bool is_valid = true;
1723 bool hyphen = false;
1724 for(int i = 0; token[i] != '\0'; i++) {
1725 const char ch = token[i];
1726 if(ch == '-') {
1727 //当前字符是连接符'-'
1728 if(hyphen) {
1729 //已经存在过连接符'-'
1730 is_valid = false;
1731 break;
1732 }
1733 hyphen = true;
1734 if(i == 0 || token[i + 1] == '\0') {
1735 //是否在字符串的开头或结尾
1736 is_valid = false;
1737 break;
1738 }
1739 if(isalpha(token[i - 1]) == 0 || isalpha(token[i + 1]) == 0) {
1740 //前后是否是字母
1741 is_valid = false;
1742 break;
1743 }
1744 } else if(token[i + 1] != '\0' && isalpha(ch) == 0) {
1745 //不是最后一个字符是否不是字母
1746 is_valid = false;
1747 break;
1748 } else if(isdigit(ch) != 0) {
1749 //是否是数字
1750 is_valid = false;
1751 break;
1752 }
1753 }
1754 if(is_valid) {
1755 count++;
1756 }
1757 }
1758 delete[] str;
1759 return count;
1760 }

1781 namespace pattern_matching_lcci {
1782 bool Solution::patternMatching(const string &pattern, const string &value) {
1783 int a_count = 0;
1784 int b_count = 0;
1785 for(const char ch: pattern) {
1786 if(ch == 'a') {
1787 a_count++;
1788 } else {
1789 b_count++;
1790 }
1791 }
1792 if(a_count == 0 || b_count == 0) {
1793 int size = 0;
1794 int count = 0;
1795 if(b_count == 0) {
1796 if(value.length() % a_count != 0) {
1797 return false;
1798 }
1799 size = value.length() / a_count;
1800 count = a_count;
1801 } else {
1802 if(value.length() % b_count != 0) {
1803 return false;
1804 }
1805 size = value.length() / b_count;
1806 count = b_count;
1807 }
1808 const string str = value.substr(0, size);
1809 for(int i = 0; i < count; i++) {
1810 auto s = value.substr(i * size, size);
1811 if(s != str) {
1812 return false;
1813 }
1814 }
1815 return true;
1816 }
1817 for(int a_size = 0; a_size <= value.length() / a_count; a_size++) {
1818 string a;
1819 string b;
1820 if((value.length() - a_size * a_count) % b_count == 0) {
1821 const int b_size = (value.length() - a_size * a_count) / b_count;
1822 string value_local = value;
1823 for(const char ch: pattern) {
1824 if(ch == 'a') {
1825 string a_local = value_local.substr(0, a_size);
1826 if(a.empty()) {
1827 a = a_local;
1828 } else if(a_local != a) {
1829 goto next_loop;
1830 }
1831 value_local = value_local.substr(a_size);
1832 } else {
1833 string b_local = value_local.substr(0, b_size);
1834 if(b.empty()) {
1835 b = b_local;
1836 } else if(b_local != b) {
1837 goto next_loop;
1838 }
1839 value_local = value_local.substr(b_size);
1840 }
1841 }
1842 if(a == b) {
1843 goto next_loop;
1844 }
1845 return true;
1846 }
1847 next_loop:;
1848 }
1849 return false;
1850 }
1851 }// namespace pattern_matching_lcci

1853 namespace map_of_highest_peak {
1854 vector<vector<int>> Solution::highestPeak(vector<vector<int>> &isWater) {
1855 const int m = isWater.size();
1856 const int n = isWater[0].size();
1857 auto *occupied = new bool *[m];
1858 for(int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
1859 occupied[i] = new bool[n];
1860 memset(occupied[i], 0, n * sizeof(bool));
1861 }
1862 auto que = queue<pair<int, int>>();
1863 for(int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
1864 for(int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
1865 if(isWater[i][j] == 1) {
1866 que.push(pair(i, j));
1867 isWater[i][j] = 0;
1868 occupied[i][j] = true;
1869 } else {
1870 isWater[i][j] = 1;
1871 }
1872 }
1873 }
1874 while(!que.empty()) {
1875 pair<int, int> current = que.front();
1876 que.pop();
1877 pair<int, int> nexts[4] = {pair(current.first + 1, current.second),
1878 pair(current.first - 1, current.second),
1879 pair(current.first, current.second + 1),
1880 pair(current.first, current.second - 1)};
1881 for(auto next: nexts) {
1882 if(0 <= next.first && next.first < m && 0 <= next.second && next.second < n && !occupied[next.first][next.second]) {
1883 isWater[next.first][next.second] = isWater[current.first][current.second] + 1;
1884 occupied[next.first][next.second] = true;
1885 que.push(next);
1886 }
1887 }
1888 }
1889 delete[] occupied;
1890 return isWater;
1891 }
1892 }// namespace map_of_highest_peak

1942 namespace all_divisions_with_the_highest_score_of_a_binary_array {
1943 vector<int> Solution::maxScoreIndices(vector<int> &nums) {
1944 const auto n = nums.size();
1945 auto left_0_count = vector<int>();
1946 auto right_1_count = vector<int>();
1947 left_0_count.push_back(0);
1948 right_1_count.push_back(0);
1949 int count = 0;
1950 for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
1951 if(nums[i] == 0) {
1952 count++;
1953 }
1954 left_0_count.push_back(count);
1955 }
1956 count = 0;
1957 for(int i = n - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
1958 if(nums[i] == 1) {
1959 count++;
1960 }
1961 right_1_count.push_back(count);

1965 for(int i = 0; i <= n; i++) {
1966 maximum = max(maximum, left_0_count[i] + right_1_count[i]);
1967 }
1968 auto ans = vector<int>();
1969 for(int i = 0; i <= n; i++) {
1970 if(maximum == left_0_count[i] + right_1_count[i]) {
1971 ans.push_back(i);
1972 }
1973 }
1974 return ans;
1975 }

1978 namespace find_substring_with_given_hash_value {
1979 string Solution::subStrHash(string s, int power, int modulo, int k, int hashValue) {
1980 power %= modulo;
1981 auto *const pn = new int[k];
1982 pn[0] = 1;
1983 for(int i = 1; i < k; i++) {
1984 pn[i] = static_cast<unsigned long long>(pn[i - 1]) * static_cast<unsigned long long>(power) % modulo;
1985 }
1986
1987 for(int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {
1988 unsigned long long hash = 0;
1989 for(int j = 0; j < k; j++) {
1990 hash += static_cast<unsigned long long>((s[i + j] - 'a' + 1) % modulo) * pn[j];
1991 hash %= modulo;
1992 }
1993 if(hash == hashValue) {
1994 return s.substr(i, k);
1995 }
1996 }
1997 delete[] pn;
1998 return "";
1999 }
2000 }// namespace find_substring_with_given_hash_value

2002 namespace groups_of_strings {
2003 vector<int> Solution::groupStrings(vector<string> &words) {
2004 auto ans = vector<int>();
2005 auto nums = vector<unsigned int>();
2006 for(const auto &word: words) {
2007 auto num = compress(word);
2008 nums.push_back(num);
2009 insert(num);
2010 }
2011 for(const auto num: nums) {
2012 for(int i = 0; i < 26; i++) {
2013 auto next = num ^ 1 << i;//添加或删除字符 i
2014 if(parent.contains(next)) {
2015 to_union(num, next);
2016 }
2017 if((num >> i & 1) == 1) {
2018 //存在字符i
2019 for(int j = 0; j < 26; j++) {
2020 if((num >> j & 1) == 0) {
2021 //不存在字符j
2022 auto next = num ^ 1 << i | 1 << j;
2023 if(parent.contains(next)) {
2024 to_union(num, num ^ 1 << i | 1 << j);// 替换字符 i 为 j
2025 }
2026 }
2027 }
2028 }
2029 }
2030 }
2031 ans.push_back(groups);
2032 ans.push_back(max_size);
2033 return ans;
2034 }
2035
2036 unsigned int Solution::compress(const string &word) {
2037 unsigned int ans = 0;
2038 for(const char ch: word) {
2039 ans |= 1 << ch - 'a';
2040 }
2041 return ans;
2042 }
2043
2044 void Solution::insert(unsigned int num) {
2045 parent.insert(pair(num, num));
2046 rank.insert(pair(num, 0));
2047 if(!size.contains(num)) {
2048 size.insert(pair(num, 1));
2049 groups++;
2050 } else {
2051 size[num]++;
2052 max_size = size[num];
2053 }
2054 }
2055
2056 unsigned int Solution::find(unsigned int x) { return x == parent[x] ? x : parent[x] = find(parent[x]); }
2057
2058 void Solution::to_union(unsigned int x1, unsigned int x2) {
2059 const int f1 = find(x1);
2060 const int f2 = find(x2);
2061 if(f1 == f2) {
2062 return;
2063 }
2064 groups--;
2065 if(rank[f1] > rank[f2]) {
2066 parent[f2] = f1;
2067 size[f1] += size[f2];
2068 max_size = max(max_size, size[f1]);
2069 } else {
2070 parent[f1] = f2;
2071 size[f2] += size[f1];
2072 max_size = max(max_size, size[f2]);
2073 if(rank[f1] == rank[f2]) {
2074 ++rank[f2];
2075 }
2076 }
2077 }

2080 namespace number_of_steps_to_reduce_a_number_to_zero {
2081 int Solution::numberOfSteps(int num) {
2082 if(num == 0) {
2083 return 0;
2084 }
2085 int count = 0;
2086 while(num != 0) {
2087 if((num & 1) == 0) {
2088 count += 1;
2089 } else {
2090 count += 2;
2091 }
2092 num >>= 1;
2093 }
2094 return count - 1;
2095 }

2098 namespace longest_nice_substring {
2099 string Solution::longestNiceSubstring(const string &s) {
2100 auto [max_start, max_len] = dfs(s, 0, s.length() - 1);
2101 if(max_len == 0) {
2102 return "";
2103 }
2104 return s.substr(max_start, max_len);
2105 }
2106
2107 pair<int, int> Solution::dfs(string s, int start, int end) {
2108 if(start == end) {
2109 return {start, 0};
2110 }
2111 int lower = 0;
2112 int upper = 0;
2113 int max_start = 0;
2114 int max_len = 0;
2115 for(int i = start; i <= end; i++) {
2116 const char ch = s[i];
2117 if(islower(ch) != 0) {
2118 lower |= 1 << ch - 'a';
2119 } else {
2120 //isupper
2121 upper |= 1 << ch - 'A';
2122 }
2123 }
2124 if(lower == upper) {
2125 //是美好字符串
2126 return {start, end - start + 1};
2127 }
2128 //不是美好字符串
2129 const int not_nice = lower ^ upper;//无法构成美好字符串的字符
2130 int i = start;
2131 while(i <= end) {
2132 if((not_nice >> tolower(s[i]) - 'a' & 1) == 1) {
2133 //在not_nice中
2134 i++;
2135 continue;
2136 }
2137 int j = i + 1;
2138 while(j <= end && (not_nice >> tolower(s[j]) - 'a' & 1) != 1) {
2139 j++;
2140 }
2141 auto [next_start, next_len] = dfs(s, i, j - 1);
2142 if(max_len < next_len) {
2143 max_len = next_len;
2144 max_start = next_start;
2145 }
2146 i = j;
2147 }
2148 return {max_start, max_len};
2149 }
2150 }// namespace longest_nice_substring

2325 namespace minimum_difference_in_sums_after_removal_of_elements {
2326 long long Solution::minimumDifference(vector<int> &nums) {
2327 const int n = nums.size() / 3;
2328 auto *left_sum = new long long[n];
2329 auto *right_sum = new long long[n];
2330 long long left_min = 0;
2331 long long right_max = 0;
2332 auto left_n = priority_queue<int>();
2333 auto right_n = priority_queue<int, vector<int>, greater<>>();
2334 for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
2335 left_n.push(nums[i]);
2336 left_min += nums[i];
2337 }
2338 for(int i = 3 * n - 1; i >= 2 * n; i--) {
2339 right_n.push(nums[i]);
2340 right_max += nums[i];
2341 }
2342 const long long left_min_preserve = left_min;
2343 const long long right_max_preserve = right_max;
2344 left_sum[0] = left_min;
2345 right_sum[n - 1] = right_max;
2346 for(int i = n; i < 2 * n; i++) {
2347 if(nums[i] < left_n.top()) {
2348 left_min += nums[i] - left_n.top();
2349 left_n.pop();
2350 left_n.push(nums[i]);
2351 }
2352 left_sum[i - n] = left_min;
2353 }
2354 for(int i = 2 * n - 1; i >= n; i--) {
2355 if(nums[i] > right_n.top()) {
2356 right_max += nums[i] - right_n.top();
2357 right_n.pop();
2358 right_n.push(nums[i]);
2359 }
2360 right_sum[i - n] = right_max;
2361 }
2362 long long ans = left_min_preserve - right_sum[0];
2363 for(int i = 0; i < n - 1; i++) {
2364 ans = min(ans, left_sum[i] - right_sum[i + 1]);
2365 }
2366 ans = min(ans, left_sum[n - 1] - right_max_preserve);
2367 delete[] left_sum;
2368 delete[] right_sum;
2369 return ans;
2370 }

2582 namespace grid_illumination {
2583 vector<int> Solution::gridIllumination(int n, vector<vector<int>> &lamps, vector<vector<int>> &queries) {
2584 auto ls = unordered_set<pair<int, int>, pair_hash>();
2585 auto row = unordered_map<int, int>();
2586 auto col = unordered_map<int, int>();
2587 auto diag_down = unordered_map<int, int>();
2588 auto diag_up = unordered_map<int, int>();
2589 for(auto lamp: lamps) {
2590 int x = lamp[0];
2591 int y = lamp[1];
2592 auto p = make_pair(x, y);
2593 if(!ls.contains(p)) {
2594 ls.insert(p);
2595 row[x]++;
2596 col[y]++;
2597 diag_down[n - x + y]++;
2598 diag_up[x + y]++;
2599 }
2600 }
2601 auto ans = vector<int>();
2602 for(auto query: queries) {
2603 int query_x = query[0];
2604 int query_y = query[1];
2605 if(row[query_x] > 0 || col[query_y] > 0 || diag_down[n - query_x + query_y] > 0 || diag_up[query_x + query_y] > 0) {
2606 ans.push_back(1);
2607 } else {
2608 ans.push_back(0);
2609 }
2610 pair<int, int> adjacents[9] = {make_pair(query_x + 1, query_y + 1), make_pair(query_x + 1, query_y), make_pair(query_x + 1, query_y - 1),
2611 make_pair(query_x, query_y + 1), make_pair(query_x, query_y), make_pair(query_x, query_y - 1),
2612 make_pair(query_x - 1, query_y + 1), make_pair(query_x - 1, query_y), make_pair(query_x - 1, query_y - 1)};
2613 for(auto adjacent: adjacents) {
2614 if(ls.contains(adjacent)) {
2615 ls.erase(adjacent);
2616 auto [x, y] = adjacent;
2617 row[x]--;
2618 col[y]--;
2619 diag_down[n - x + y]--;
2620 diag_up[x + y]--;
2621 }
2622 }
2623 }
2624 return ans;
2625 }

3062 namespace pancake_sorting {
3063 vector<int> Solution::pancakeSort(vector<int> &arr) {
3064 auto ans = vector<int>();
3065 const int n = arr.size();
3066 auto *current = new int[n];
3067 auto *sorted = new int[n];
3068 for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
3069 current[i] = arr[i];
3070 sorted[i] = arr[i];
3071 }
3072 sort(sorted, sorted + n);
3073 RESTART:
3074 for(int i = n - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
3075 if(current[i] != sorted[i]) {
3076 const int target = sorted[i];
3077 int target_i = -1;
3078 for(int j = 0; j <= i; j++) {
3079 if(current[j] == target) {
3080 target_i = j + 1;
3081 break;
3082 }
3083 }
3084 if(target_i == 1) {
3085 target_i = i + 1;
3086 }
3087 ans.push_back(target_i);
3088 for(int j = 0; j < target_i / 2; j++) {
3089 swap(current[j], current[target_i - j - 1]);
3090 }
3091 goto RESTART;
3092 }
3093 }
3094 delete[] current;
3095 delete[] sorted;
3096 return ans;
3097 }

3426 for(int mask = mask_max - 1; mask > 0; mask--) {
3427 if((mask & subset) == subset) {
3428 f[mask] = (f[mask] + static_cast<long long>(f[mask ^ subset]) * freq[i]) % mod;
3429 }
3430 }
3431 }
3432 int ans = 0;
3433 for(int mask = 1; mask < mask_max; mask++) {
3434 ans = (ans + f[mask]) % mod;
3435 }
3436 return ans;
3437 }
3438 }// namespace the_number_of_good_subsets

3502 }

3505 current_y--;

3612 long long Solution::minimumTime(vector<int> &time, int totalTrips) {

3628 return r;

3631 r = m;

3633 l = m;

3640 namespace minimum_time_to_finish_the_race {
3641 int Solution::minimumFinishTime(vector<vector<int>> &tires, int changeTime, int numLaps) {
3642 /* min_times[i] = 用一个轮胎跑 i 圈的最小花费 */
3643 vector<long long> min_times(20, 1e9);
3644 for(auto &v: tires) {
3645 const long long f = v[0];
3646 const long long r = v[1];
3647 const long long cost = f + changeTime;
3648 long long current = f;
3649 long long sum = cost;
3650 for(int i = 1; i <= 19; i++) {
3651 min_times[i] = min(min_times[i], sum);
3652 current *= r;
3653 if(current > cost) {
3654 current = f;
3655 sum += cost;
3656 } else {
3657 sum += current;
3658 }
3659 }
3660 }
3661 /* dp[i] = 跑 i 圈的最小花费 */
3662 vector<long long> dp(numLaps + 1, 1e9);
3663 dp[0] = 0;
3664 for(int i = 1; i <= numLaps; i++) {
3665 for(int j = 1; j <= min(19, i); j++) {
3666 dp[i] = min(dp[i], dp[i - j] + min_times[j]);
3667 }
3668 }
3669 /* 最后需要减去一次换轮胎的时间 */
3670 return dp[numLaps] - changeTime;
3671 }
3672 }// namespace minimum_time_to_finish_the_race

3675 int Solution::maximumRequests(int n, vector<vector<int>> &requests) {
3676 int ans = 0;

3678 auto *in = new int[n];
3679 auto *out = new int[n];

3685 in[requests[j][1]]++;
3686 }

3690 if(out[j] != in[j]) {
3691 ok = false;
3692 break;
3693 }
3694 }
3695 if(ok) {
3696 ans = max(ans, popcount(i));

3746 namespace find_the_closest_palindrome {
3747 string Solution::nearestPalindromic(const string &n) {
3748 const long long num = stoll(n);
3749 if(num == 10 || num == 11) {
3750 return "9";
3751 }
3752 if(num < 10) {
3753 return to_string(num - 1);
3754 }
3755 int len = n.length();
3756 const bool even = n.length() % 2 == 0;
3757 string prefix = n.substr(0, n.length() / 2 + (even ? 0 : 1));
3758 string option_str[3];
3759 auto rev = string(prefix.rbegin() + (even ? 0 : 1), prefix.rend());
3760 option_str[2] = prefix + rev;
3761 const long long prefix_int[2] = {stoll(prefix) - 1, stoll(prefix) + 1};
3762 string prefix_str[2] = {to_string(prefix_int[0]), to_string(prefix_int[1])};
3763 for(int i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
3764 if(prefix_str[i].length() == prefix.length()) {
3765 rev = string(prefix_str[i].rbegin() + (even ? 0 : 1), prefix_str[i].rend());
3766 option_str[i] = prefix_str[i] + rev;
3767 } else if(prefix_str[i].length() > prefix.length()) {
3768 rev = string(prefix_str[i].rbegin() + (even ? 1 : 2), prefix_str[i].rend());
3769 option_str[i] = prefix_str[i] + rev;
3770 } else if(prefix_str[i].length() < prefix.length()) {
3771 rev = string(prefix_str[i].rbegin(), prefix_str[i].rend());
3772 option_str[i] = prefix_str[i] + (even ? "9" : "") + rev;
3773 }
3774 }
3775 long long option_int[3] = {stoll(option_str[0]), stoll(option_str[1]), stoll(option_str[2])};
3776 sort(option_int, option_int + 3);
3777 long long minimum = option_int[0];
3778 for(int i = 1; i < 3; i++) {
3779 if(abs(option_int[i] - num) < abs(minimum - num) && option_int[i] != num) {
3780 minimum = option_int[i];
3781 }
3782 }
3783 return to_string(minimum);
3784 }

3857 namespace all_ancestors_of_a_node_in_a_directed_acyclic_graph {
3858 vector<vector<int>> Solution::getAncestors(int n, vector<vector<int>> &edges) {
3859 for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
3860 nexts[i] = unordered_set<int>();
3861 ancestors[i] = set<int>();
3862 }
3863 for(auto edge: edges) {
3864 nexts[edge[0]].insert(edge[1]);
3865 }
3866 for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
3867 for(const auto next: nexts[i]) {
3868 auto *dfsd = new bool[n];
3869 memset(dfsd, 0, n * sizeof(bool));
3870 dfs(dfsd, i, next);
3871 delete[] dfsd;
3872 }
3873 }
3874 vector<vector<int>> ans;
3875 for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
3876 vector<int> vec;
3877 for(auto i: ancestors[i]) {
3878 vec.push_back(i);
3879 }
3880 ans.push_back(vec);
3881 }
3882 return ans;
3883 }

3889 if(!dfsd[next]) {
3890 dfs(dfsd, v, next);

4090 int left = query[0];
4091 int right = query[1];
4092 auto li = lower_bound(candle_pos.begin(), candle_pos.end(), left);
4093 if(li == candle_pos.end() || *li > right) {
4094 ans.push_back(0);
4095 continue;
4096 }
4097 auto ri = lower_bound(candle_pos.rbegin(), candle_pos.rend(), right, greater<int>());
4098 if(ri == candle_pos.rend() || *ri < left) {
4099 ans.push_back(0);
4100 continue;
4101 }
4102 ans.push_back(plate_count[*ri] - plate_count[*li]);
4103 }
4104 return ans;
4105 }
4106 }// namespace plates_between_candles

4109 int Solution::bestRotation(vector<int> &nums) {

4111 vector k_score_diff(n + 1, 0);
4112 for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
4113 const int low = (i + 1) % n;
4114 const int high = (i - nums[i] + n) % n;
4115 k_score_diff[low]++;
4116 k_score_diff[high + 1]--;

4118 k_score_diff[0]++;
4119 k_score_diff[n]--;
4120 }

4126 score += k_score_diff[i];
4127 if(score > max_score) {
4128 ans = i;
4129 max_score = score;
4130 }
4131 }
4132 return ans;
4133 }

4152 int Solution::countHighestScoreNodes(vector<int> &parents) {
4153 int ans = 0;
4154 auto nodes = vector<TreeNode *>(parents.size(), nullptr);
4155 auto edges = vector(parents.size(), vector<int>());
4156 auto scores = vector<unsigned long long>(parents.size(), 0);
4157 for(int i = 0; i < parents.size(); i++) {
4158 nodes[i] = new TreeNode(i);
4159 if(parents[i] != -1) {
4160 edges[i].push_back(parents[i]);
4161 edges[parents[i]].push_back(i);
4162 }

4164 TreeNode *root = nullptr;
4165 for(int i = 0; i < parents.size(); i++) {
4166 if(parents[i] != -1) {
4167 nodes[parents[i]]->add_child(nodes[i]);
4168 } else {
4169 root = nodes[i];
4170 }
4171 }
4172 root->dfs();

4174 for(int i = 0; i < parents.size(); i++) {

4177 for(const auto *child: node->get_children()) {
4178 score *= child->get_count();

4180 if(node->get_parent() != nullptr) {
4181 score *= root->get_count() - node->get_count();
4182 }
4183 max_score = max(max_score, score);
4184 scores[i] = score;
4185 }

4225 namespace max_area_of_island {
4226 int Solution::maxAreaOfIsland(vector<vector<int>> &grid) {
4227 const int m = grid.size();
4228 const int n = grid[0].size();
4229 auto uf = UnionFind(m, n);
4230 int ans = 0;
4231 for(int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
4232 for(int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
4233 if(grid[i][j] == 1) {
4234 const pair<int, int> p = make_pair(i, j);
4235 ans = max(ans, uf.get_size(p));
4236 pair<int, int> siblings[4] = {
4237 make_pair(i + 1, j),
4238 make_pair(i - 1, j),
4239 make_pair(i, j + 1),
4240 make_pair(i, j - 1),
4241 };
4242 for(const auto sibling: siblings) {
4243 if(uf.contains(sibling) && grid[sibling.first][sibling.second] == 1 && !uf.same(p, sibling)) {
4244 uf.merge(p, sibling);
4245 ans = max(ans, uf.get_size(p));
4246 }
4247 }
4248 }
4249 }
4250 }
4251 return ans;
4252 }
4253
4254 UnionFind::UnionFind(int m, int n)
4255 : m(m), n(n) {
4256 parent = unordered_map<pair<int, int>,
4257 pair<int, int>,
4258 function<unsigned int(const pair<int, int> &)>>(
4259 m * n,
4260 [](const pair<int, int> &p) { return static_cast<unsigned int>(p.first * 50 + p.second); });
4261 size = unordered_map<pair<int, int>,
4262 int,
4263 function<unsigned int(const pair<int, int> &)>>(
4264 m * n,
4265 [](const pair<int, int> &p) { return static_cast<unsigned int>(p.first * 50 + p.second); });
4266 rank = unordered_map<pair<int, int>,
4267 int,
4268 function<unsigned int(const pair<int, int> &)>>(
4269 m * n,
4270 [](const pair<int, int> &p) { return static_cast<unsigned int>(p.first * 50 + p.second); });
4271 for(int i = 0; i < m; i++) {
4272 for(int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
4273 pair<int, int> p = make_pair(i, j);
4274 parent[p] = p;
4275 size[p] = 1;
4276 rank[p] = 0;
4277 }
4278 }
4279 }
4280
4281 pair<int, int> UnionFind::find(pair<int, int> val) {
4282 if(parent[val] != val) {
4283 parent[val] = find(parent[val]);
4284 }
4285 return parent[val];
4286 }
4287
4288 void UnionFind::merge(pair<int, int> a, pair<int, int> b) {
4289 const auto pa = find(a);
4290 const auto pb = find(b);
4291 if(pa != pb) {
4292 const int sum = size[pa] + size[pb];
4293 if(rank[pa] > rank[pb]) {
4294 parent[pb] = pa;
4295 } else {
4296 parent[pa] = pb;
4297 if(rank[pa] == rank[pb]) {
4298 ++rank[pb];
4299 }
4300 }
4301 size[pa] = sum;
4302 size[pb] = sum;
4303 }
4304 }
4305
4306 bool UnionFind::same(pair<int, int> a, pair<int, int> b) { return find(a) == find(b); }
4307
4308 bool UnionFind::contains(pair<int, int> p) const { return parent.contains(p); }
4309
4310 int UnionFind::get_size(pair<int, int> p) { return size[find(p)]; }

4403 namespace minimum_weighted_subgraph_with_the_required_paths {
4404 long long Solution::minimumWeight(int n, vector<vector<int>> &edges, int src1, int src2, int dest) {
4405 auto *graph = new vector<pair<int, int>>[n];
4406 auto *graph_rev = new vector<pair<int, int>>[n];
4407 for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
4408 graph[i] = vector<pair<int, int>>();
4409 graph_rev[i] = vector<pair<int, int>>();
4410 }
4411 for(auto &edge: edges) {
4412 auto from = edge[0];
4413 auto to = edge[1];
4414 auto weight = edge[2];
4415 graph[from].emplace_back(to, weight);
4416 graph_rev[to].emplace_back(from, weight);
4417 }
4418
4419 long long a = LLONG_MAX;
4420 vector dist_src1(n, LLONG_MAX);
4421 vector dist_src2(n, LLONG_MAX);
4422 vector dist_dest(n, LLONG_MAX);
4423
4424 calc_dist(src1, graph, dist_src1);
4425 calc_dist(src2, graph, dist_src2);
4426 calc_dist(dest, graph_rev, dist_dest);
4427
4428 long long ans = LLONG_MAX;
4429
4430 for(int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {
4431 if(dist_src1[i] != LLONG_MAX && dist_src2[i] != LLONG_MAX && dist_dest[i] != LLONG_MAX) {
4432 ans = min(ans, dist_src1[i] + dist_src2[i] + dist_dest[i]);
4433 }
4434 }
4435 if(ans == LLONG_MAX) {
4436 ans = -1;
4437 }
4438 delete[] graph;
4439 delete[] graph_rev;
4440 return ans;
4441 }
4442
4443 void Solution::calc_dist(int s, vector<pair<int, int>> *graph, vector<long long int> &dist) {
4444 priority_queue<pair<long long, int>, vector<pair<long long, int>>, greater<>> pq;
4445 dist[s] = 0;
4446 pq.emplace(0, s);
4447 while(!pq.empty()) {
4448 auto [weight, node] = pq.top();
4449 pq.pop();
4450 if(weight > dist[node]) {
4451 continue;
4452 }
4453 for(auto [next_node, next_weight]: graph[node]) {
4454 if(weight + next_weight < dist[next_node]) {
4455 dist[next_node] = weight + next_weight;
4456 pq.emplace(weight + next_weight, next_node);
4457 }
4458 }
4459 }
4460 }

4471 //11110xxx

4474 //1110xxxx
4475 len.push_back(3);
4476 } else if(num >> 5 == 6) {

4478 len.push_back(2);

4481 len.push_back(-1);

4483 return false;
4484 }

4486 int count = 0;
4487 for(int i = 0; i < len.size(); i++) {
4488 if(count != 0) {
4489 if(len[i] != -1) {
4490 return false;
4491 }
4492 } else {
4493 count = len[i];
4494 if(count == -1) {
4495 return false;
4496 }
4497 }
4498 count--;
4499 }
4500 return count == 0;

4749 namespace minimum_white_tiles_after_covering_with_carpets {
4750 int Solution::minimumWhiteTiles(string floor, int numCarpets, int carpetLen) {
4751 const int n = floor.length();
4752 vector f(numCarpets + 1, vector<int>(n));
4753 f[0][0] = floor[0] % 2;
4754 for(int i = 1; i < n; ++i) {
4755 f[0][i] = f[0][i - 1] + floor[i] % 2;
4756 }
4757 for(int i = 1; i <= numCarpets; ++i) {
4758 // j < carpetLen 的 f[i][j] 均为 0
4759 for(int j = carpetLen; j < n; ++j) {
4760 f[i][j] = min(f[i][j - 1] + floor[j] % 2, f[i - 1][j - carpetLen]);
4761 }
4762 }

4816 vector<int> Solution::maximumBobPoints(int numArrows, vector<int> &aliceArrows) {

4823 if((n & 1 << i) != 0) {
4824 score += 11 - i;
4825 rest -= aliceArrows[11 - i] + 1;
4826 }

4829 }

4835 NEXT_N:;

4840 numArrows -= aliceArrows[11 - i] + 1;
4841 ans[11 - i] = aliceArrows[11 - i] + 1;
4842 }

4849 namespace the_time_when_the_network_becomes_idle {
4850 int Solution::networkBecomesIdle(vector<vector<int>> &edges, vector<int> &patience) {
4851 unordered_map<int, Node *> um;
4852 unordered_set<int> nodes;
4853 for(int i = 0; i < patience.size(); i++) {
4854 um[i] = new Node(i, patience[i]);
4855 nodes.insert(i);
4856 }
4857 for(auto edge: edges) {
4858 um[edge[0]]->linked.insert(edge[1]);
4859 um[edge[1]]->linked.insert(edge[0]);
4860 }
4861 auto comp = [](const pair<int, int> &s1, const pair<int, int> &s2) -> bool { return s1.second > s2.second; };
4862 priority_queue<pair<int, int>, vector<pair<int, int>>, decltype(comp)> pq;
4863 pq.push(make_pair(0, 0));
4864 while(!nodes.empty()) {
4865 auto [num, len] = pq.top();
4866 pq.pop();
4867 if(nodes.contains(num)) {
4868 nodes.erase(num);
4869 Node *node = um[num];
4870 node->time = len;
4871 for(auto next: node->linked) {
4872 if(nodes.contains(next)) {
4873 pq.push(make_pair(next, len + 1));
4874 }
4875 }
4876 }
4877 }
4878 int ans = 0;
4879 for(auto [num, node]: um) {
4880 if(num != 0) {
4881 int resent_num = node->time * 2 / node->patience;
4882 if(node->time * 2 % node->patience == 0) {
4883 resent_num--;
4884 }
4885 ans = max(ans, resent_num * node->patience + 2 * node->time + 1);
4886 }
4887 }
4888 return ans;
4889 }
4890 }// namespace the_time_when_the_network_becomes_idle
